"""
# GC Async UDP I/O

GC async UDP is a compatibility facade over the no-GC async UDP backend
library. That no-GC async facade exposes both the ready-future async socket and
the underlying sync datagram socket type.

Keeping this module as a facade prevents the GC library family from declaring
its own UDP runtime hooks. Platform-specific UDP behavior belongs below the
no-GC backend boundary.
"""

export use std.nogc_async_mut.io.udp.{UdpSocket, AsyncUdpSocket}
